Title: The Forward Push
Description:
<Sharnax scratches her chin.>

The commander was right. The Primalists are calling reinforcements from the elemental planes.

<Sharnax smirks.>

It would be a shame if something happened to their gateways, $c.
ObjectivesText: Obtain Misttouched, Earthen, and Iceforged gateway stones, and close the 3 elemental gateways.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak with Sharnax at Gelikyr Overlook.
RewardText: Looks like you made it in one piece.
